356
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:19,490
Benefactor?

357
00:18:20,900 --> 00:18:22,000
Thank you for your help!

358
00:18:22,260 --> 00:18:22,790
By the way,

359
00:18:23,730 --> 00:18:24,740
to repay you,

360
00:18:24,810 --> 00:18:25,730
