[Li Yan, the emperor of Great Chen]

396
00:20:11,980 --> 00:20:12,790
Yes.

397
00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:23,180
Your subject, Lu Changkong,

398
00:20:24,030 --> 00:20:24,900
