427
00:21:47,700 --> 00:21:48,750
It's alright.

428
00:21:48,980 --> 00:21:50,140
What do you want?

429
00:21:50,310 --> 00:21:51,080
Tell me.

430
00:21:55,260 --> 00:21:57,740
I'm the emperor of Great Chen.

431
00:21:58,470 --> 00:22:00,680
